{"kanda":6,"sarga":34,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"अथतांजातन्तापांतेनवाक्येनमोहिताम् ।सरमाह्लादयामासमहींघौरीमिवाम्भसा","trans":"Thus, Sita's agony was put off by Saarana's consoling words and Sita was glad just as the parched earth was delighted with shower of rain.","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"and thus"},{"d":"जातसन्तापाम्","m":"put off the agony"},{"d":"तेनवाक्येन","m":"by her words"},{"d":"मोदिताम्","m":"gladdened"},{"d":"ताम्","m":"that"},{"d":"सरमा","m":"Saarana"},{"d":"घौरीम्","m":"parched"},{"d":"महीम्","m":"earth"},{"d":"अम्भसाइव","m":"like rainwater"},{"d":"समाह्लादयामास","m":"consoled and delighted."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"ततस्तस्याहितंसख्याश्चिकीर्षन्तीसखीवचः ।उवाचकालेकालज्ञास्मितपूर्वाभिभाषिणी","trans":"Then Saarana who knew the right time to do so, wishing the welfare of her dear friend Sita and desirous of doing anything for her smiled before she started speaking.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"कालज्ञा","m":"who knows the time to do"},{"d":"स्मितपूर्वाभिभाषिणी","m":"who smiles before talking"},{"d":"सखी","m":"friend"},{"d":"सख्याः","m":"beloved"},{"d":"तस्याः","m":"her"},{"d":"हितम्","m":"welfare"},{"d":"चिकीर्षन्ती","m":"desirous of doing anything"},{"d":"काले","m":"in time"},{"d":"वचः","m":"these words"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"उत्सहेयमहंगत्वात्वद्वाक्यमसितेक्षणे: ।निवेद्यकुशलंरामेप्रतिच्छन्नानिवर्तितुम्","trans":"\"Darkeyed Sita! I am eager to go (to Rama's presence) and communicate your welfare and message. I can return back hidden (from Ravana's view).\"","words":[{"d":"असितेक्षणे","m":"dark eyed lady"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"प्रतिच्छन्ना","m":"hidden"},{"d":"गत्वा","m":"going"},{"d":"त्वद्वाक्यम्","m":"your message"},{"d":"कुशलम्","m":"welfare"},{"d":"रामे","m":"to Rama"},{"d":"निवेद्य","m":"communicate"},{"d":"निवर्तितुम्","m":"return back"},{"d":"उत्सहेयम्","m":"eager."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"नहिमेक्रममाणायानिरालम्बेविहायसि ।समर्थोगतिमन्वेतुंपवनोगरुडोऽपिवा","trans":"\"While I fly through the sky without any support, either the wind god or even Garuda will not be capable of following my movement.\"","words":[{"d":"निरालम्बे","m":"without any support"},{"d":"विहायसि","m":"going through the sky"},{"d":"क्रममाणायाः","m":"proceeding"},{"d":"मे","m":"me"},{"d":"गतिम्","m":"movement"},{"d":"अन्वेतुम्","m":"to follow"},{"d":"पवनः","m":"wind god"},{"d":"गरुडोऽपिवा","m":"or even Garuda"},{"d":"नसमर्थः","m":"not capable."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"एवंब्रुवाणांतांसीतासरमांपुनरब्रवीत् ।मधुरंश्लक्क्षणयावाचापूर्वशोकाभिपन्नया","trans":"When Saarana was telling Sita in that way, Sita's face which was earlier filled with tears became pleasant and she spoke again.","words":[{"d":"सीता","m":"Sita"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that manner"},{"d":"ब्रुवाणाम्","m":"telling"},{"d":"तांसरमाम्","m":"that Saarana"},{"d":"पूर्वशोकाभिपन्नया","m":"earlier filled with tears"},{"d":"श्लक्क्षणया","m":"gentle countenance"},{"d":"वाचा","m":"spoke"},{"d":"मधुरम्","m":"sweet"},{"d":"पुनः","m":"again"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"said."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"समर्थागगनंगन्तुमपिवात्वंरसातलम् ।अवगच्छाम्यकर्तव्यंकर्तव्यंतेमदन्तरे","trans":"\"You are capable of flying through the sky or even going to the underworld. For my sake you will do what cannot be done also and that it is your bounden duty, is also known to me.\"","words":[{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"गगनम्","m":"in the sky"},{"d":"अपिच","m":"even"},{"d":"रसातलम्","m":"underworld"},{"d":"समर्था","m":"capable"},{"d":"अकर्तव्यम्","m":"that which can't be done"},{"d":"मदन्तरे","m":"for my sake"},{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"कर्तव्यम्","m":"duty"},{"d":"एवगच्छामि","m":"also known to me."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"मत्प्रियंयदिकर्तव्यंयदिबुद्धि: स्थिरातव ।ज्ञातुमिच्छामितंगत्वाकिंकरोतीतिरावणः","trans":"\"In my opinion, your duty for me is to go and find out what Ravana is doing now, if you are firmly resolved.\"","words":[{"d":"मप्रतियम्","m":"in my opinion"},{"d":"कर्तव्यंयदि","m":"What you should do"},{"d":"तव","m":"your"},{"d":"बुद्धिः","m":"understood"},{"d":"स्थिरायदि","m":"resolved firmly"},{"d":"रावणः",