्वा","m":"went"},{"d":"समन्त्रिणः","m":"with ministers"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"their"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"कथितम्","m":"talk"},{"d":"शुश्राव","m":"heard."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"साश्रुत्वानिश्चयंतस्यनिश्चयज्ञादुरात्मनः ।पुनरेवागमत्क्षिप्रमशोकवनिकांशुभाम्","trans":"Having heard and known the intention of evilminded Ravana, she (Saarana) quickly reached the beautiful Ashoka grove.","words":[{"d":"निश्चयज्ञा","m":"known the intention"},{"d":"सा","m":"of him, Ravana"},{"d":"दुरात्मनः","m":"evil minded"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"निश्चयम्","m":"decision"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"heard"},{"d":"क्षिप्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"पुनरेव","m":"once again"},{"d":"शुभाम्","m":"beautiful"},{"d":"अशोकवनिकाम्","m":"Ashoka grove"},{"d":"आगमत्","m":"reached."}]},{"v":16,"dev":"साप्रविष्टाततस्तत्रददर्शजनकात्मजाम् ।प्रतीक्षमाणांस्वामेवभ्रष्टपद्मामिवश्रियम्","trans":"On entering the Ashoka grove, she saw the daughter of Janaka eagerly waiting for her every moment, looking like Lord Vishnu's wife Lakshmi, who lost her lotus seat.","words":[{"d":"प्रविष्टा","m":"having entered"},{"d":"सा","m":"she"},{"d":"तत्र","m":"then"},{"d":"स्वामेव","m":"for her"},{"d":"प्रतीक्षमाणाम्","m":"waiting eagerly every moment"},{"d":"भ्रष्टपद्माम्","m":"one who lost the lotus seat"},{"d":"जनकात्मजाम्","m":"daughter of Janaka"},{"d":"ददर्श","m":"saw."}]},{"v":17,"dev":"तांतुसीतापुनःप्राप्तांसरमांवल्गुभाषिणीम् ।परिष्वज्यचसुस्निग्धंददौचस्वयमासनम्","trans":"On seeing the kind Saarana returning, Sita was very glad. She embraced her and offered a seat herself.","words":[{"d":"सीता","m":"Sita"},{"d":"पुनः","m":"again"},{"d":"प्राप्ताम्","m":"returning"},{"d":"वल्गुभाषिणीम्","m":"who spoke kindly"},{"d":"सरमाम्","m":"Saarana"},{"d":"सुस्निग्धम्","m":"very glad"},{"d":"परिष्वज्य","m":"embraced"},{"d":"स्वयम्","m":"herself"},{"d":"आसनम्","m":"seat"},{"d":"ददौ","m":"offered."}]},{"v":18,"dev":"इहासीनासुखंसर्वमाख्याहिममतत्त्वतः ।क्रूरस्यनिश्चयंतस्यरावणस्यदुरात्मनः","trans":"\"Seated here happily reveals to me truly that cruel and evil minded Ravana's intention.\"","words":[{"d":"इह","m":"here"},{"d":"सुखम्","m":"happily"},{"d":"आसीना","m":"seated"},{"d":"क्रूरस्य","m":"cruel one"},{"d":"दुरात्मनः","m":"evil minded one"},{"d":"तस्यरावणस्य","m":"that Ravana's"},{"d":"निश्चयम्","m":"intention"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"in toot"},{"d":"मम","m":"to me"},{"d":"तत्त्वतः","m":"truly"},{"d":"आख्याहि","m":"reveal to me."}]},{"v":19,"dev":"एवमुक्तातुसरमासीतयावेपमानया ।कथितंसर्वमाचष्टेरावणस्यसमन्त्रिणः","trans":"To the trembling Sita, Saarana narrated totally all the discussion Ravana had with the ministers.","words":[{"d":"वेपमानया","m":"trembling"},{"d":"सीतया","m":"to Sita"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"like that"},{"d":"उक्ता","m":"said"},{"d":"सरमा","m":"Saarana"},{"d":"समन्त्रिणः","m":"with the ministers"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"totally"},{"d":"कथितम्","m":"all the discussion"},{"d":"आचष्टे","m":"narrated."}]},{"v":20,"dev":"जनन्याराक्षसेन्द्रोवैत्वन्मोक्षार्थंबृहद्वचः ।अविद्धेनचवैदेहिमन्त्रिवृद्धेनबोधितः","trans":"\"O Vaidehi! Ravana's mother Kaikasi and the aged minister Aviddha advised the Lord of Rakshasas to release you.\"","words":[{"d":"वैदेहि","m":"Vaidehi"},{"d":"त्वन्मोक्षार्थम्","m":"to release you"},{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्रः","m":"Lord of Rakshasa's"},{"d":"जनन्या","m":"mother"},{"d":"मन्त्रिवृद्धेव","m":"aged minister"},{"d":"अविद्धेन","m":"Aviddha"},{"d":"बृहत्","m":"long"},{"d":"वचः","m":"words"},{"d":"बोधितः","m":"advised."}]},{"v":21,"dev":"दीयतामभिसत्कृत्यमनुजेन्द्रायमैथिली ।निदर्शनंतेपर्याप्तंजनस्थानेयदद्भुतम्","trans":"\"Let Mythili be given back to the ruler of the people (Rama) offering good hospitality. The (killing of fourteen thousand Rakshasas) amazing performance at Janasthana by Rama should serve as sufficient proof to you (of the consequences).\"","words":[{"d":"मनुजेन्द्राय","m":"ruler of people"},{"d":"अभिसत्कृत्य","m":"extending good hospitality"},{"d":"मैधिली","m":"Mythili"},{"d":"दीयताम्","m":"given back"},{"d":"जनस्थाने","m":"at Janasthana"},